item.title: I used the wayback machine to digg up old info
item.dc:creator: @dexto dexto
item.description:
@dexto wrote:

By breaking the rules you will possibly pay a fine and if you cannot pay the fine then you will give the clan an item of the value in place of the fine. If you keep breaking the rules of the BlacKnights or continuously cannot pay a fine given to you, then there will be a reward put on your head and you will be killed. Your gaming life will be hell, and if you want to be a baby and change characters, go ahead, we don't want to run into you anymore; we do not want our time wasted.

don’t you just love reading that, the game was way harder to play then it is nowadays and remember, we were all about 13 - 15 year olds, it should be other way around haha xD
